getPSDELogicNodes.name: 未完成
getPSDELogicNodes.sql:
select
	COUNT(1) as status_0
from
	hr_exam he
where
	he.STATUS = 10
	and he.CREATE_UID = ?

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 已完成
getPSDELogicNodes.sql:
SELECT COUNT(1) as status_1
FROM hr_exam he 
WHERE he.STATUS = 20 and he.CREATE_UID = ?
